'''Accademia Italiana Thailand''' is a fashion and design institute founded in 2006 in [[Bangkok]]'s [[Watthana District]]. It is an offshoot of the [[Accademia italiana]]. Students successfully completing the three-year program are awarded the diploma of the Accademia Italiana and a bachelor's degree (BA) from [[Nottingham Trent University]].

